com.eim.utility.statistics.model
Class BenchmarkRelatedStatistics

java.lang.Object
  com.eim.utility.statistics.model.BenchmarkRelatedStatistics
All Implemented Interfaces:
IStatistics, java.io.Serializable
@Entity
public class BenchmarkRelatedStatistics
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, IStatistics

POJO representing the benchmark related statistics.

It is annotated with hibernate annotations for persistence purpose.
These statistics are persisted in the table STATS_BENCHMARK and identified using a sequence called SEQ_STATS_BENCHMARK. That POJO possesses 7 fields (other than the id field) that are mandatory:

  • targetEntityType
  • targetEntityId
  • relatedEntityType
  • relatedEntityId
  • applicationDate
  • computationDate
  • status
